text: Any recommendations for cleaning burn marks off of laser cut acrylic?

elements.text: Any recommendations for cleaning burn marks off of laser cut acrylic?

text:
Potentially a bit of acetone or isopropyl alcohol will clean it. If I remember correctly I made a cut for you on frosted acrylic that had slight burn marks?

That usually happens when the paper on the acrylic is taken off both sides prior to cutting (we're supposed to leave it on the back). I believe your cut came from a piece of scrap that had it mistakenly removed
